# <type>(<scope>): <short description> [PRD-XXX/CC-X or DEC-XXX]
#
# Types: feat, fix, docs, test, refactor, chore, research
# Scope: module name (positioning, regime, market_pricing, etc.)
#
# Body: explain what and why (not how)
#
# Footer: references, breaking changes, superseded decisions
#
# Example:
# feat(market_pricing): add US rates ingestion [PRD-200/CC-1]
#
# Adds fredapi-based pipeline for DGS2 and DFII2 series.
# Produces us_rates.parquet with daily data from 2015.
#
# Refs: PRD-200
